title: Iowa DOT, Incorporated Cities, Iowa, 1990
name: Iowa DOT, Incorporated Cities, Iowa, 1990
description:
Abstract:
    This coverage contains arcs and points that represent the boundaries of the 953 incorporated cities and towns in Iowa. The data was obtained from the Iowa DOT and is current to the summer 1992. This coverage also has interior boundaries of unincorporated areas within city boundaries. 
Purpose:
    This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.
